  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'While Sleeping' is a first-person horror game about experiencing sleep paralysis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are sleeping to go to work tomorrow, and you get sleep paralysis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your body is paralyzed and you can't move, and you can't do anything except look around or close your eyes and open them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to survive until daybreak by experiencing ghosts and creepy phenomena that appear around you while you are sleeping paralyzed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playtime: Average 15 ~ 30 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Caution: To create a scary atmosphere, some of the details may be exaggerated compared to actual sleep paralysis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Sleep Paralysis</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/be55286bf16d9796feb6af16f87aceb7.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/be55286bf16d9796feb6af16f87aceb7.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/be55286bf16d9796feb6af16f87aceb7.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You can't move your body. You can only open or close your eyes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Creepy Phenomenon</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/d3cee1bf2d4e1a4b71f8c5eb37ba98ea.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/d3cee1bf2d4e1a4b71f8c5eb37ba98ea.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/d3cee1bf2d4e1a4b71f8c5eb37ba98ea.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Creepy phenomena continue to appear as time passes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Don't get caught by ghosts</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/cf2da45de95fe0b00e640f31163f2fed.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/cf2da45de95fe0b00e640f31163f2fed.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/cf2da45de95fe0b00e640f31163f2fed.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Each ghost that appears has a different way you should act.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Survive until the sun rises</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/85ca37c31f0ca34becb0e53eb87ffef1.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/85ca37c31f0ca34becb0e53eb87ffef1.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/85ca37c31f0ca34becb0e53eb87ffef1.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You have to survive until you get out of sleep paralysis.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'While Sleeping' is a first-person horror game about experiencing sleep paralysis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are sleeping to go to work tomorrow, and you get sleep paralysis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your body is paralyzed and you can't move, and you can't do anything except look around or close your eyes and open them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to survive until daybreak by experiencing ghosts and creepy phenomena that appear around you while you are sleeping paralyzed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playtime: Average 15 ~ 30 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Caution: To create a scary atmosphere, some of the details may be exaggerated compared to actual sleep paralysis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Sleep Paralysis</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/be55286bf16d9796feb6af16f87aceb7.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/be55286bf16d9796feb6af16f87aceb7.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/be55286bf16d9796feb6af16f87aceb7.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You can't move your body. You can only open or close your eyes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Creepy Phenomenon</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/d3cee1bf2d4e1a4b71f8c5eb37ba98ea.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/d3cee1bf2d4e1a4b71f8c5eb37ba98ea.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/d3cee1bf2d4e1a4b71f8c5eb37ba98ea.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Creepy phenomena continue to appear as time passes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Don't get caught by ghosts</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/cf2da45de95fe0b00e640f31163f2fed.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/cf2da45de95fe0b00e640f31163f2fed.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/cf2da45de95fe0b00e640f31163f2fed.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Each ghost that appears has a different way you should act.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Survive until the sun rises</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/85ca37c31f0ca34becb0e53eb87ffef1.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/85ca37c31f0ca34becb0e53eb87ffef1.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/85ca37c31f0ca34becb0e53eb87ffef1.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You have to survive until you get out of sleep paralysis.</p>"